      • addEventListener

        public void addEventListener(CefDevToolsClient.EventListener eventListener)
        Add an event listener for DevTools protocol events. Events by default are disabled and need to be enabled on a per domain basis, e.g. by sending Network.enable to enable network related events.(为DevTools协议事件添加事件监听器。默认情况下，事件被禁用，需要根据每个域启用，例如通过发送Network. connect来启用网络相关事件。)
        Parameters:
        eventListener - the listener to add(eventSYS-要添加的监听器)

      • executeDevToolsMethod

        public java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.lang.String> executeDevToolsMethod(java.lang.String method)
        Execute a method call over the DevTools protocol. See the DevTools protocol documentation for details of supported methods and the expected syntax for parameters.

        If an error occurs the returned future is completed exceptionally, otherwise its value is asynchronously set to the method result.

        Call #addEventListener(String, EventListener) to subscribe to events.

        (通过DevTools协议执行方法调用。有关支持的方法和参数预期语法的详细信息，请参阅 DevTools协议文档。如果发生错误，返回的future将异常完成，否则其值将被同步设置为方法结果。调用#addEventSYS（字符串，EventSYS）订阅事件。)
        Parameters:
        method - the method name(方法-方法名称)
        Returns:
        return a future with the method result if the method was executed successfully(如果方法执行成功，则返回带有方法结果的future)

      • executeDevToolsMethod

        public java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.lang.String> executeDevToolsMethod(java.lang.String method,
                                                                                      java.lang.String parametersAsJson)
        Execute a method call over the DevTools protocol. See the DevTools protocol documentation for details of supported methods and the expected syntax for parameters.

        If an error occurs the returned future is completed exceptionally, otherwise its value is asynchronously set to the method result.

        Call #addEventListener(String, EventListener) to subscribe to events.

        (通过DevTools协议执行方法调用。有关支持的方法和参数预期语法的详细信息，请参阅 DevTools协议文档。如果发生错误，返回的future将异常完成，否则其值将被同步设置为方法结果。调用#addEventSYS（字符串，EventSYS）订阅事件。)
        Parameters:
        method - the method name(方法-方法名称)
        parametersAsJson - JSON object with parameters, or null if no parameters are needed(parametersAsJson -带有参数的SON对象，如果不需要参数，则为空)
        Returns:
        return a future with the method result if the method was executed successfully(如果方法执行成功，则返回带有方法结果的future)
